Item ID5309

Yanillian seeds may be used by a player with level 16 Farming to grow Yanillian hops, used in creating Wizard's Mind Bombs and as payment to protect a growing Mahogany tree. Four seeds can be planted in one of the hops patches located around Gielinor. When planted, Yanillian seeds yield 14.5 Farming experience. Yanillian seeds may be obtained by pickpocketing a Master Farmer or Martin the Master Gardener.

A nearby gardener will watch over yanillian hops for 1 basket of tomatoes.

'''Yanillian seeds''' may be used by a player with level 16 [[Farming]] to grow [[Yanillian hops]], used in creating [[Wizard's Mind Bomb]]s and as payment to protect a growing [[Mahogany]] tree. Four [[seeds]] can be planted in one of the [[Farming/Patch locations#Hops patches|hops patches]] located around Gielinor. When planted, Yanillian seeds yield 14.5 [[Farming]] experience. Yanillian seeds may be obtained by pickpocketing a [[Master Farmer]] or [[Martin the Master Gardener]].

A nearby gardener will watch over yanillian hops for 1 [[Tomatoes|basket of tomatoes]].
